  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, whisk together flour, sugar, baking powder, and salt.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together milk, eggs, mustard, and chopped pickled beet.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until just combined.",
    "Gently fold in the haddock, onion, and parsley.",
    "Heat a large non-stick skillet or tava over medium heat.",
    "When the skillet is hot, drop the batter by 1/4 cupfuls onto the skillet.",
    "Cook the pancakes for 4-5 minutes, until bubbles appear on the surface and the edges are golden.",
    "Flip the pancakes and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until golden brown."
  ],
